item.title: Gran Canaria Day 1 & 2
item.description: My head is still buzzing from all the activity here at Gran Canaria. This is both my first time at GUADEC, and in Europe. That, combined with all the different people I’ve been meeting and conversations I’ve been having, has my head spinning in a good way. I’ve really gotten a kick out of meeting people, and the reactions I get: I’m the GNOME Journal guy. Please come see me, I need writers!
